**`getUsage()`**

获取当前使用量统计。

:::TuffCodeBlock{lang="ts"}
---
code: |
  const usage = await accountSDK.getUsage()
  // {
  //   aiRequestsToday: 123,
  //   aiRequestsThisMonth: 2456,
